Searchable Codebook for AllofUs

Source: vignettes/searchable_codebook.Rmd
searchable_codebook.Rmd

This table consists of mapped rows from the publicly available AllofUs Survey Codebook to the AllofUs PPI Vocabulary available on Athena. A small number of rows did not match between the codebook and the Athena PPI Vocabulary. The code to generate a full table can be found here.
